 rel="noopener">此处预订/预存</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-horrors-fat-dog-and-sprints-lead-dot-to-dot-festival-2025-line-up-buy-tickets-3814949">The Horrors、Fat Dog 和 Sprints 带领 2025 年 Dot To Dot Festival 阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《海绵宝宝》作曲家安迪·佩利去世，享年 72 岁https://www.nme.com/news/tv/spongebob-squarepants-composer-andy-paley-dies-ged-72-3814943?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=spongebob-squarepants-composer-andy-paley-dies- 72岁Damian JonesFri, 22 Nov 2024 10:09:08 +0000 NewsTV News.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3814943 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安迪·佩利和海绵宝宝" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>布莱恩·威尔逊 (Brian Wilson) 是第一批向佩利致敬的人之一，他曾与佩利合作制作 1988 年的个人复出专辑</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/spongebob-squarepants-composer-andy-paley-dies-aged-72-3814943">《海绵宝宝》作曲家安迪·佩利去世，享年 72 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安迪·佩利和海绵宝宝" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_andypaley_sponebob_getty_sky_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《海绵宝宝》作曲家安迪·佩利去世，享年 72 岁。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/spongebob-squarepants-the-cosmic-shake-review-3389100">《海绵宝宝：宇宙震动》评论：有趣</a></strong></li></ul><p>多年来，佩利还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-wilson">布莱恩·威尔逊</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jerry-lee-lewis">杰里·李·刘易斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ramones">雷蒙斯乐队</a>、麦当娜、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madonna">埃尔顿</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">·约翰</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/patti-smith">帕蒂·史密斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/debbie-harry">黛比·哈利</a>等艺术家合作过，佩利在与癌症作斗争后于周三（11 月 20 日）去世。</p><p>威尔逊是最早向这位已故作曲家致敬的人之一，佩利在 1988 年为他的个人复出专辑制作并共同创作了歌曲。</p><p>他在官方 Instagram 上发布的帖子写道：“得知布莱恩的朋友兼合作者安迪·佩利去世的消息，我们深感悲痛。安迪 (Andy) 凭借 1988 年广受好评的专辑《布莱恩·威尔逊》(Brian Wilson) 开始了他的独唱生涯，这对他的个人生涯确实起到了重要作用。</p><p> “安迪演奏电吉他和原声吉他、贝斯、鼓、打击乐器、键盘、口琴，并提供和声。他与他人共同创作了其中三首歌曲，其中包括《Rio Grande》。安迪再次与布莱恩合作创作了传奇的、未发行的 Wilson-Paley Sessions，共有二十多首歌曲。布莱恩总是称他为“天才安迪·佩利”。我们向安迪的家人和朋友表达爱和怜悯。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCoMIGhOYbB/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; bo