g@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dr-dre-snoop-dogg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dr-dre-snoop-dogg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">Snoop Dogg</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dr-dre">Dr. Dre</a>发布了一首充满活力的新单曲“Outta Da Blue”——请在下面收听。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/pa-salieu-afrikan-alien-review-3812957">Pa Salieu – 《非洲外星人》评论：一次赋权和振奋人心的回归</a></strong></li></ul><p>《Outta Da Blue》摘自他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-and-dr-dre-announce-missionary-album-release-date-3808480">即将发行的专辑《Missionary》</a> ，标志着该项目的首次预览，这将是继 Snoop 1993 年首张专辑《Doggystyle》之后，这两位说唱偶像首次在一个完整的项目中重聚。</p><p>史努比在开场诗中唱道：“<em>瓶子和母狗，相信我们重回正轨/强烈推荐我抽的狗屎/这是给我所有挑战极限的黑鬼的</em>”。</p><p>这首歌还包括 Dre 的歌词，主唱 Alus 也参与了合唱，他插入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/m.i.a">MIA</a>的《Paper Planes》。下面请聆听 Snoop Dogg 和 Dr. Dre 的《Outta Da Blue》。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Snoop Dogg - Outta Da Blue（feat. Dr. Dre &amp; Alus）[官方音频]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JUPLv48_exc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该专辑将于 12 月 13 日通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-is-now-officially-the-owner-of-death-row-records-3158014">他于 2022 年收购的传奇嘻哈唱片公司</a>Death Row Records 发行。该片将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-doggs-and-dr-dres-missionary-album-expected-for-november-release-will-feature-sting-3784246">包括斯汀在内</a>的众多明星出演。</p><p> Dre <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-doggs-and-dr-dres-missionary-album-expected-for-november-release-will-feature-sting-3784246">此前曾表示，他希望发行日期为 11 月</a>，并解释说《Missionary》与《Doggystyle》不同，因为：“这张专辑的歌词和我的音乐会展现出不同程度的成熟度。我觉得这是我职业生涯中做过的最好的音乐之一。”</p><p> Dre 博士在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-red-hot-chili-peppers-and-snoop-dogg-perform-at-olympics-closing-ceremony-3782753">为洛杉矶 2028 年奥运会交接庆祝活动（参加活动的还有 Billie Eilish 和 Red Hot Chili Peppers）表演</a>后接受<a href="https://www.etonline.com/dr-dre-shares-how-his-magical-olympics-performance-with-snoop-dogg-came-together-exclusive-230336" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《今夜娱乐》</em></a>采访时透露，他与 Snoop 的关系远不止在录音室里录制音乐。 </p><figure id="attachment_3784247" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784247" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784247" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dr-dre-snoop-dogg@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="Dr. Dre 和 Snoop Dogg 将于 2022 年 2 月 12 日星期六在 SoFi 体育场举行的超级碗 LVI 中场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dr-dre-snoop-dogg@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dr-dre-snoop-dogg@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dr-dre-snoop-dogg@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dr-dre-snoop-dogg@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dr-dre-snoop-dogg@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dr-dre-snoop-dogg@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3784247" class="wp-caption-text">德雷博士和史努比狗狗。图片来源：Robert Gauthier / 洛杉矶时报 via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>他透露：“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dr-dre-says-he-doesnt-feel-comfortable-performing-without-snoop-dogg-3783137">如果没有史努比，我什至都感觉不舒服</a>。”我和史努比之间的协同作用真的很有趣。”他接着补充道：“真的，史努比，他是超级巨星。当我们登上舞台时，我是联合主演。我们在录音室的时候感觉不一样，你知道吗？当我们在工作室时，我是队长，但当我们出去时，史努比就是那个人。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-on-meeting-sexyy-red-for-the-first-time-you-got-star-power-3813392">史努比最近还谈到了第一次见到性感红并告诉她“你有明星力量”</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-may-have-earned-9million-from-olympic-appearances-3784808">据报道，他在今年巴黎奥运会上抢尽风头的滑稽动作还为他赚了 900 万美元（710 万英镑）</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-snoop-dogg-and-dr-dre-boisterous-new-single-outta-da-blue-3814908">聆听 Snoop Dogg 和 Dr. Dre 热闹的新单曲“Outta Da Blue”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
